snippet.title: Vermin Gameplay - Nintendo Game & Watch
snippet.description:
Moles pop out of the ground and try to get into the player's garden. The player has to hit the moles with a hammer to keep them out of the garden. 

If you need a stand to display your game, take a look of the stands I use http://www.addingoil.com/store
